10000

coef <- data.frame(coef_rank = 0L,

for(i in 2:10001){
  coef[i-1,1] <- r_ds[[i]]$coefficients[[2]]
  coef[i-1,2] <- r_ds[[i]]$coefficients[[3]]
}
